dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Muros, sheet 9. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 43.0000. South Decimal Degree 42.0000. East Decimal Degree -9.0000. West Decimal Degree -10.0000. Alternate title: Muros, Spain: La Coruna Province. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Spain, 1:100,000, Estado Mayor del Ejercito, sheet 22, 1915 and sheet 42, 1919; Spain 1:200,000, Cuartel General del Generalisimo, sheet 11, 1935 and sheet 21, 1934; Spain and Portugal, Road Map 1:400,000, AMS, Third Edition, sheet 41, 1942; Railways in Spain and Portugal 1:1,500,000, GSGS, 1941, corrected from intelligence Reports, 1942-44. Partially revised from aerial photography, 1942.".
